---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Entry Requirements" description="RACP Basic Training entry requirements, selection criteria, and eligibility.">
  <div class="page-header">
    <h1>Entry Requirements</h1>
    <p>What you need before you can forge anything.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <h2>Training Application</h2>
    <p>
      Trainees must submit a training application via the College's Training Management Platform (TMP)
      prior to commencing training, at the start of the Foundation phase.
    </p>
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-title">Application deadlines</div>
      <p>28 February &nbsp;/&nbsp; 31 August</p>
    </div>
    <p>The application confirms you meet eligibility criteria and identifies the Director of Physician Education who will oversee your training.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <h2>Entry Criteria</h2>
    <ul class="item-list">
      <li>A Basic Training position in an RACP-accredited training setting or network</li>
      <li>
        General medical registration with the Medical Board of Australia
        <span class="tag">AU</span>
      </li>
      <li>
        Medical registration with a general scope of practice with the MCNZ
        <span class="tag">NZ</span>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <h2>Selection Criteria</h2>
    <ul class="item-list">
      <li>A commitment and capability to pursuing a career as a physician or paediatrician</li>
      <li>The ability to plan and manage their learning</li>
      <li>Communication</li>
      <li>Cultural competence</li>
      <li>Ethics and professional behaviour</li>
      <li>Leadership, management, and teamwork</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</Layout>
